  </div>


  <div class="top-buttons" id="topMenu">
    <a href="/student/notes">üìö Notes</a>
    <a href="https://mediaforges.blogspot.com/">üìù Blog</a>
    <a href="/resume-builder" target="_blank">üíª Resume Builder</a>
    <a href="https://www.w3schools.com/" target="_blank">üîó W3 Schools</a>
